{"tid":2091831,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"GAP關一半分店 醞釀撤出香港  客人：國安法影響營商環境","createTime":"2020-07-03T01:40:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T03:16:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9610fb8e1bfe230ee4176993d3e49bf65109c947","tid":2091831,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T01:40:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200703/V6M2AHVSYTMTPMT4S2CQ5L6AUE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200703%2FV6M2AHVSYTMTPMT4S2CQ5L6AUE%2F&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBE6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=40390dce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200703%2FV6M2AHVSYTMTPMT4S2CQ5L6AUE%2F&h=c25bc896\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200703/V6M2AHVSYTMTPMT4S2CQ5L6AUE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\nGAP關一半分店 醞釀撤出香港 <br />\n客人：國安法影響營商環境<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【經營困境】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本地零售業陷於低氣壓，美國休閒服裝品牌GAP有關舖行動。昨日GAP尖沙嘴旗艦店及銅鑼灣希慎廣場分店貼上「關店清倉」宣傳告示，消息指，尖沙嘴旗艦店營業至本月底，該舖正於市場每月叫價150萬元放租，料GAP將退租，而GAP尖沙嘴K11 MUSEA的兩分店亦傳即將關閉，料該品牌有一半分店關門，醞釀退出香港市場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/nY0ncAwMyac10s48kjsLvvmzVzo=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/52OQTOHRBZ3L4PWH4SGMTHAJPA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnY0ncAwMyac10s48kjsLvvmzVzo%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F52OQTOHRBZ3L4PWH4SGMTHAJPA.jpg&h=3f2c7165&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGAP加連威老道旗艦店外已貼上「關店清倉」告示，店員指該店最快本月底關閉。<br />\n<br />\n記者昨在GAP各門店所見，加連威老道旗艦店及希慎廣場兩店門外已貼上「關店清倉」，內容為該店將「停止營業」，顧客可到其他分店和網店購物。本月前，店內已設全場貨品五折優惠，最新擴大至四折促銷清貨。<br />\n<br />\n加連威老道店門兩邊的扶手電梯已經關閉，客人出入要使用中間的<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n顧客現時在相關分店購買的貨物，日後不能到其他分店退換。<br />\n<br />\n屬該品牌常客的余小姐表示，常買GAP的牛仔褲或襯衫，但認為GAP是「<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n安法，市民喪失自由，相信會影響外國對香港營商環境信心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4月曾指無足夠現金流<br />\n<br />\n回顧當年GAP在香港中環開店時，場面墟冚，開業不足一小時已擠<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n三層樓面以330萬元放租。<br />\n<br />\nGAP在尖沙嘴K11 MUSEA的B227號舖和301A號舖也設有分店，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n又一城、屯門V City，以及東涌東薈城的分店及Outlet。<br />\n<br />\nGAP今年4月曾發警告指，受武漢肺炎疫情影響，集團<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n年下跌43%至21.07億美元（約163.3億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n香港經濟環境<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n有ESPRIT和Forever 21等。"},{"pid":"86eda8e1211aceb83cc7c3d8b356e0bdb64fbd30","tid":2091831,"uid":259083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T01:45:52.000Z","msg":"其實GAP不嬲都做得差,最近北美d分店都收皮。好彩kayne west 肯救佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82918afe60097e4a6726184351869b60bcf89ad6","tid":2091831,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T01:47:28.000Z","msg":"淨底未關果d分店，我諗係提早解約要賠太多"},{"pid":"38fdbeb487bca611ec08ab6bea22c3d5c851553f","tid":2091831,"uid":198539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T01:47:58.000Z","msg":"以後買牛仔褲邊到買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c2858938db0c176a765170f6dc6cb4ef5819bc7","tid":2091831,"uid":11447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38fdbeb487bca611ec08ab6bea22c3d5c851553f","tid":2091831,"uid":198539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T01:47:58.000Z","msg":"以後買牛仔褲邊到買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T01:48:39.000Z","msg":"China Eagle<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c2ec7b341a80c339d3371602d56b07d402fb09","tid":2091831,"uid":226466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T01:49:31.000Z","msg":"唔關國安法/新冠肺炎事<br />\n<br />\n係因為佔中/黑暴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de7bcc892fa9f01f3ac99e56224a25fea7e13ed2","tid":2091831,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"ci